01:17:24.311 --> 01:17:26.104
Nema milosti, tribune.

01:17:26.939 --> 01:17:28.482
To si ti učio.

01:17:28.941 --> 01:17:30.442
Loša lekcija.

01:17:32.027 --> 01:17:33.320
Dajem ti učitelja.

01:17:36.448 --> 01:17:38.283
Pusti njih da prođu.

01:17:45.958 --> 01:17:47.417
Nazarećanin?

01:17:48.418 --> 01:17:49.795
Nestao je.

01:17:55.509 --> 01:17:56.969
Ovdje nema neprijatelja.

01:17:59.179 --> 01:18:00.389
Ovdje preko!

01:18:03.308 --> 01:18:06.645
Držiš svijet u svojim rukama, Beneficijariju.

01:18:07.646 --> 01:18:09.064
Znaj to.

01:18:10.899 --> 01:18:12.109
Ja vjerujem

01:18:13.152 --> 01:18:15.112
da on počiva u ovim ljudima.

01:18:33.172 --> 01:18:35.007
Danas nitko neće umrijeti.

01:18:38.760 --> 01:18:39.887
Nitko.

01:18:49.688 --> 01:18:50.856
Nastavi hodati.

01:18:52.691 --> 01:18:54.151
Nemoj ništa govoriti.

01:18:55.986 --> 01:18:57.362
Zapamti ovo.

01:19:58.298 --> 01:20:00.008
Zašto misliš ovdje?

01:20:00.092 --> 01:20:04.680
Ovdje nas je pozvao da ga slijedimo.
Ponekad je teško prepoznati ga.

01:20:05.097 --> 01:20:07.349
Šimune! Šimune!

01:20:08.809 --> 01:20:11.061
Šimune, oni žele jesti.

01:20:21.530 --> 01:20:23.115
Onda idemo loviti ribu.

01:20:24.074 --> 01:20:26.285
Idemo loviti ribu! Hajde!

01:20:26.368 --> 01:20:28.245
Dođite! Idemo!

01:20:28.787 --> 01:20:30.080
On će nas pronaći!

01:20:35.002 --> 01:20:36.128
Hajde.

01:21:10.204 --> 01:21:13.165
Mi smo ovdje.

01:21:15.709 --> 01:21:16.835
Braćo,

01:21:18.837 --> 01:21:20.714
idemo loviti ribu!

01:21:24.426 --> 01:21:28.055
Vucite. Tako.

01:22:00.963 --> 01:22:02.464
Da bacimo ponovno?

01:22:08.470 --> 01:22:09.888
Još dvaput.

01:22:10.556 --> 01:22:12.599
A onda spavaj dok te sunce ne probudi.

01:22:46.633 --> 01:22:47.968
Je li bilo neke sreće?

01:22:51.096 --> 01:22:53.098
Probajte ponovno s desne strane.

01:23:02.733 --> 01:23:03.901
Ne.

01:23:14.077 --> 01:23:16.371
Braćo, Andrija. Krenite.

01:23:16.455 --> 01:23:18.165
-Što se događa?
-Pripremi mrežu, Ivane!

01:23:18.248 --> 01:23:19.708
-Probudi se.
-Filipe, brate.

01:23:19.791 --> 01:23:21.919
Raširite se. Pripremite mrežu.

01:23:29.968 --> 01:23:31.178
Bacajte.

01:23:41.772 --> 01:23:43.565
-Što se dogodilo?
-Diži.

01:23:43.649 --> 01:23:47.027
-Preplitko smo!
-Upravo jesmo! Zaglavili smo!

01:23:47.110 --> 01:23:50.864
-Diži mrežu, Andrija.
-Zapela je za nešto.

01:23:50.948 --> 01:23:53.033
-To je riba.
-Zapela je na dnu.

01:23:53.116 --> 01:23:54.827
-Ne mičemo se!
-To je riba.

01:23:56.954 --> 01:23:58.247
To je riba.

01:24:02.000 --> 01:24:03.377
To je riba!

01:24:06.213 --> 01:24:07.506
Riba!

01:24:08.882 --> 01:24:10.634
Kako si znao?

01:24:12.386 --> 01:24:13.679
Vjera!

01:24:14.847 --> 01:24:16.890
Jahve!

01:24:16.974 --> 01:24:20.394
-To je bio on!
-Jahve!

01:24:24.148 --> 01:24:25.691
Jahve!

01:24:27.985 --> 01:24:29.361
Braćo.

01:24:30.737 --> 01:24:33.198
To je on!

01:24:51.258 --> 01:24:53.218
-Dodaj drugima.
-Hvala ti, Petre.

01:24:58.056 --> 01:24:59.766
-Vode?
-Ne, hvala.

01:25:00.476 --> 01:25:03.437
Brate? Brate, voda.

01:25:21.246 --> 01:25:23.248
Jesi li znao da će on uskrsnuti?

01:25:25.000 --> 01:25:27.503
Rekao je da hoće,

01:25:28.253 --> 01:25:30.547
ali, istinu govoreći, sumnjali smo.

01:25:35.719 --> 01:25:37.679
Zašto ste ga onda pratili?

01:25:38.722 --> 01:25:40.599
Gubavče! Miči se!

01:25:41.683 --> 01:25:42.768
Makni se odavde!

01:25:43.435 --> 01:25:44.603
Miči se!

01:25:46.814 --> 01:25:48.982
Gubavac! Gubavac!

01:25:49.066 --> 01:25:50.192
-Gubavac!
-Van!

01:25:50.275 --> 01:25:53.111
-Van!
-Van! Van!

01:25:53.779 --> 01:25:56.240
Izlazi van! Gubavac!

01:25:56.323 --> 01:25:57.825
Gubavac!

01:26:17.928 --> 01:26:19.138
Učinit će to.

01:26:19.680 --> 01:26:21.014
Što?

01:26:21.849 --> 01:26:23.350
Iscijeliti će tog čovjeka.

01:26:25.769 --> 01:26:27.062
Kako?

01:26:27.688 --> 01:26:29.690
Samo gledaj.

01:26:31.150 --> 01:26:33.110
Nitko me nikada ne dotiče.

01:26:33.193 --> 01:26:34.486
Čudo.

01:26:35.112 --> 01:26:36.738
Vidjeli smo ih mnogo puta, Rimljanine.

01:26:56.258 --> 01:26:57.718
Imaš li vjere?

01:26:58.844 --> 01:27:00.220
Dođi, ustani.

01:27:38.509 --> 01:27:39.802
Braćo.

01:27:45.557 --> 01:27:46.934
Eto zato.

01:28:17.464 --> 01:28:19.133
Što tražite?

01:28:20.843 --> 01:28:23.804
Nevolju, ona će doći.

01:28:25.222 --> 01:28:27.808
Ovo njima prijeti.

01:28:28.392 --> 01:28:30.686
Pilatu, Kajfi i Rimu.

01:28:31.895 --> 01:28:33.730
Onda nevolje dolaze i ovim putem.

01:28:34.523 --> 01:28:36.066
Imaj vjeru, tribune.

01:28:56.670 --> 01:28:59.548
Petre, idemo još malo dalje hodati.

01:29:01.049 --> 01:29:02.551
Zašto?

01:29:02.634 --> 01:29:04.178
Da budemo bliže.

01:29:05.137 --> 01:29:06.972
Šimune, voliš li me još?

01:29:08.015 --> 01:29:10.642
Da, znaš da te volim.

01:29:12.436 --> 01:29:14.938
-Voliš li me?
-Da.

01:29:15.814 --> 01:29:18.984
-Šimune, voliš li me?
-Svim svojim srcem.

01:29:19.526 --> 01:29:21.612
Onda moraš nahraniti moje jaganjce.

01:30:59.877 --> 01:31:02.004
Čak ne znam ni što bih pitao.

01:31:05.883 --> 01:31:07.759
Govori iz srca.

01:31:09.136 --> 01:31:12.598
Ne mogu sve ovo pomiriti

01:31:15.142 --> 01:31:17.060
sa svijetom koji poznajem.

01:31:18.562 --> 01:31:21.648
Vidio si svojim očima, a opet sumnjaš.

01:31:23.025 --> 01:31:26.653
Zamisli sumnje onih koji nisu nikada vidjeli.
S time se oni suočavaju.

01:31:30.157 --> 01:31:31.992
Što te plaši?

01:31:36.246 --> 01:31:37.831
Da griješim.

01:31:39.166 --> 01:31:41.335
Zalažem vječnost za to.

01:31:43.128 --> 01:31:44.546
Pa, onda,

01:31:46.256 --> 01:31:47.716
upoznaj Ga.

01:31:56.183 --> 01:31:57.684
Kada si umro,

01:32:03.023 --> 01:32:04.608
ja sam bio prisutan.

01:32:10.197 --> 01:32:11.406
Pomagao sam.

01:32:12.157 --> 01:32:13.534
Znam.

01:32:21.875 --> 01:32:24.670
Što je to što tražiš, Klavije?

01:32:26.964 --> 01:32:29.842
Sigurnost? Mir?

01:32:31.677 --> 01:32:33.595
Dan bez smrti?

01:33:19.683 --> 01:33:21.518
Probudite se, braćo!

01:33:21.602 --> 01:33:24.021
-Braćo, probudite se. Jakove, nestao je!
-Probudite se.

01:33:24.104 --> 01:33:25.189
-Nestao je.
-Što?

01:33:25.272 --> 01:33:26.690
-Jahve je nestao.
-Ivane, probudi se.

01:33:26.773 --> 01:33:28.358
-Braćo!
-Jahve!

01:33:28.442 --> 01:33:31.069
-Gdje je on?
-Dođite, braćo.

01:33:31.153 --> 01:33:33.739
-Kamo je nestao?
-Jahve!

01:33:33.822 --> 01:33:36.158
-Jahve!
-Gdje je on?

01:33:36.241 --> 01:33:38.410
-Jahve!
-Jahve!

01:33:38.494 --> 01:33:40.954
-Jahve!
-Brate!

01:33:53.967 --> 01:33:55.093
Braćo.

01:34:04.520 --> 01:34:06.980
Idem spremiti mjesto za vas.

01:34:09.274 --> 01:34:10.484
Idite

01:34:11.193 --> 01:34:14.029
po cijelom svijetu i propovijedajte evanđelje

01:34:14.738 --> 01:34:16.448
svim narodima.

01:34:17.491 --> 01:34:20.244
Vi ćete biti moji svjedoci u Jeruzalemu

01:34:20.828 --> 01:34:24.706
i cijeloj Judeji i Samariji
i do kraja cijelog svijeta.

01:34:30.379 --> 01:34:32.756
I znajte da ću biti s vama.

01:34:33.757 --> 01:34:35.092
Uvijek.

01:35:02.828 --> 01:35:03.871
Gospodine?

01:35:30.689 --> 01:35:33.317
Ne radi se samo o vječnom životu.

01:35:33.400 --> 01:35:37.696
Već i kako se živi život,
po maču ili po ljubavi.

01:35:38.113 --> 01:35:41.158
I to vas mijenja ovdje.

01:35:41.241 --> 01:35:42.409
Vrijeme je.

01:35:42.493 --> 01:35:43.744
Zbogom, braćo.

01:35:44.328 --> 01:35:46.747
-To je zapravo prilično dobro.
-Prelijepo je.

01:35:46.830 --> 01:35:48.665
