Amen.

01:35:49.958 --> 01:35:51.126
Amen.

01:35:51.210 --> 01:35:52.961
-Zbogom, braćo.
-Mir s vama, braćo.

01:35:53.045 --> 01:35:54.087
Zbogom.

01:35:54.171 --> 01:35:56.757
-Do sljedećeg susreta u njegovom prisustvu.
-Zbogom, brate.

01:36:00.260 --> 01:36:02.304
-Bog te blagoslovio, Petre.
-Zbogom.

01:36:06.016 --> 01:36:07.476
-Pazite na sebe, braćo.
-Pazi se.

01:36:07.559 --> 01:36:09.061
Zbogom, braćo.

01:36:15.484 --> 01:36:16.777
Priključi nam se, tribune.

01:36:19.988 --> 01:36:21.865
Jeruzalem samo donosi nevolje.

01:36:22.491 --> 01:36:28.038
Nevolje i ovaj duh koje je obećao. Pozvani
smo da ga ovdje primimo, Rimljanine.

01:36:28.121 --> 01:36:29.289
Tvoj poziv je da loviš ribu.

01:36:30.833 --> 01:36:33.293
Da, za ljude.

01:36:36.630 --> 01:36:38.715
Kako sada mogu raditi bilo što drugo?

01:36:42.094 --> 01:36:43.971
Hoćeš li i ti biti ribar, Klavije?

01:36:54.314 --> 01:36:55.649
Onda,

01:36:56.316 --> 01:36:57.776
zbogom, brate.

01:36:59.820 --> 01:37:01.155
Zbogom.

01:37:04.783 --> 01:37:06.618
Neka te Bog blagoslovi i čuva.

01:37:16.253 --> 01:37:18.005
