01:37:22.009 --> 01:37:23.385
Uvijek.

01:37:29.933 --> 01:37:32.519
Petre, dođi!

01:37:32.603 --> 01:37:34.146
Braćo!

01:37:35.898 --> 01:37:37.065
Petre!

01:37:37.149 --> 01:37:38.317
Brate!

01:37:39.067 --> 01:37:40.194
Čekajte!

01:37:48.869 --> 01:37:50.329
Ovuda?

01:38:32.412 --> 01:38:35.082
Sumnjam da ćemo ikada više čuti za njih.

01:38:47.010 --> 01:38:48.345
Tribune?

01:39:07.489 --> 01:39:08.866
Plaćam ovim.

01:39:11.493 --> 01:39:12.619
Tribune,

01:39:15.539 --> 01:39:17.791
vjeruješ li istinski u sve ovo?

01:39:25.048 --> 01:39:26.300
Vjerujem

01:39:28.719 --> 01:39:30.762
